OL,3,CPensioner jailed for killing baby by
OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,FA pensioner has been jailed after
OL,7,Fcausing the death of an eight-month-
OL,8,Fold baby after her car crashed into
OL,9,Fher pram outside a hospital in
OL,10,FPembrokeshire.
OL,12,FBridget Curtis, 71, from Begelly
OL,13,Fkilled Mabli Cariad Hall outside
OL,14,FWithybush Hospital in June 2023.
OL,16,FCurtis, who had previously pleaded
OL,17,Fguilty to causing death by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving, was sentenced to four years
OL,19,Fbehind bars at Swansea Crown Court on
OL,20,FThursday 23 January.
