OL,3,CPensioner jailed for killing baby by
OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,FShe has also been disqualified from
OL,7,Fdriving for eight years.
OL,9,FThe court heard how Bridget Curtis was
OL,10,Ftaking her daughter for an appointment
OL,11,Fat Withybush Hospital in Haverfordwest
OL,12,Fand had stopped the car at a drop off
OL,13,Fpoint on 21 June 2023.
OL,15,FWhen her daughter got out and went to
OL,16,Fretrieve her handbag from the rear
OL,17,Fseat, Curtis turned to help her.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
