OL,3,CPensioner jailed for killing baby by
OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,FIt was at that point Curtis lost
OL,7,Fcontrol of the vehicle which
OL,8,Faccelerated forwards colliding with a
OL,9,Fgroup of people waiting in the grounds.
OL,11,FThe car struck a pram which had eight-
OL,12,Fmonth-old Mabli in it, who later died
OL,13,Fof her injuries.
OL,15,FSpeaking at court, Mabli's parents
OL,16,Fsaid their entire family had been
OL,17,F"broken and destroyed" by Curtis'
OL,18,Factions on that day and that they
OL,19,Fwould never get over the grief of
OL,20,Flosing their baby.
