OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "As a family
OL,7,Fwe wish to thank Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,8,Fand everyone else involved in securing
OL,9,Fjustice for Mabli today.
OL,11,F"It's been a harrowing 19 months to
OL,12,Freach this point, but we appreciate
OL,13,Fhow complicated these investigations
OL,14,Fare to ensure the right outcome.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
