OL,3,CPensioner jailed for killing baby by
OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,F"We now have to navigate the rest of
OL,7,Four lives without our baby girl, Mabli
OL,8,FCariad, who made our family so
OL,9,Fcomplete. As parents, we have to
OL,10,Fcontinue to support our other children
OL,11,Fto deal with their deep grief, a grief
OL,12,Fwhich we share every moment of every
OL,13,Fday.
OL,15,F"Mabli Cariad was the sunshine in our
OL,16,Flives and shall forever be loved and
OL,17,Fmissed.
