OL,3,CPensioner jailed for killing baby by
OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,F"If anything is to be learned from the
OL,7,Funnecessary loss of Mabli's life, it
OL,8,Fis that everyone who sits behind the
OL,9,Fwheel of a vehicle needs to realise
OL,10,Fthat they are responsible for their
OL,11,Fown actions and the wellbeing of
OL,12,Fothers."
OL,14,FAfter a police investigation, Curtis
OL,15,Fwas charged with causing death by
OL,16,Fdriving dangerously on 24 July 2024.
OL,17,FShe appeared at Swansea Crown Court on
OL,18,F20 September 2024, where she pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty.
