OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,FAs well as being jailed and
OL,7,Fdisqualified from driving, Curtis will
OL,8,Falso have to pass an extended re-test
OL,9,Fbefore she is able to drive again.
OL,11,FIn sentencing Curtis, HHJ Geraint
OL,12,FWalters said Mabli's life was taken
OL,13,F"senselessly and needlessly", adding
OL,14,Fthat it was hard to imagine a case
OL,15,F"more grossly reckless" than this.
