OL,4,Ccrashing into her pram
OL,6,FSergeant Sara John, of Dyfed-Powys
OL,7,FPolice's Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit, said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts remain with Mabli's family
OL,10,Fwho have had to endure the pain of
OL,11,Flosing her in these tragic and
OL,12,Fcompletely avoidable circumstances.
OL,14,F"This was a difficult investigation
OL,15,Fand we are grateful to Mabli's family
OL,16,Ffor their patience and dignity as they
OL,17,Fwaited for this outcome today."
