OL,6,FMichael Cray of the CPS said: "Bridget
OL,7,FCurtis tried to look for a handbag on
OL,8,Fthe rear seat whilst still controlling
OL,9,Fthe vehicle's pedals.
OL,11,F"As a result, she lost control of the
OL,12,Fcar injuring bystanders and causing
OL,13,Fthe death of a baby.
OL,15,F"Curtis' actions had fatal
OL,16,Fconsequences and serve as a reminder
OL,17,Fto all motorists of the serious
OL,18,Fresponsibilities that come with being
OL,19,Fa driver.
